               <msContents>
                  <summary>Images. F. irv: crude drawings of birds. 1r-11v: Image of Saint Mary,
                     Chaine Repertoire 172, beginning, ሰላም ሰላም ለዝክረ ስምኪ ሐዋዝ. <locus target="#11v">Fols. 11v, </locus>
                     mentions the scribe ገብረአብ. F<locus target="#12r">12r, </locus>-21v: Image of Jesus Christ,
                     Mälk‘a Iyyäsus, መልክአ፡ ኢየሱስ፡. Répertoire 123. <locus target="#22r">22r</locus>: note of
                     ownership, አባ ድሮም</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="2r" to="11v" facs="002">Fols 2r–11v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2891RepCh172">beginning, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰላም ሰላም ለዝክረ ስምኪ ሐዋዝ</foreign></title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="12r" to="21v" facs="012">Fols 12r–21v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2839RepCh123">beginning, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰላም ለዝክረ ስምከ ሰመ መሐላ ዘኢይሄሱ</foreign></title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
